item.description:
The spelling Bee doesn't begin until 9PM (I know, kinda late for a monday night, but...)

Hang out before hand, have some drinks, grab some food from the AS220 Foo(d) counter and see if any of our members are willing to spell strange words in front of a crowd. Free to Watch.

Last year we had 2 members enter the competition (limited number of participants, get there early to register if you want in, costs $5) and make it to the third round.
item.name: Drinks and the "Not About the Buildings" Spelling Bee @ AS220
